fields.name: Dr. Amit Verma
fields.bio: Dr. Amit Verma is a renowned cardiologist with 15 years of experience specializing in treating heart-related ailments.

fields.name: Dr. Priya Sen
fields.bio: Dr. Priya Sen is an expert dermatologist, known for her work in cosmetic treatments and skincare solutions.

fields.name: Dr. Suresh Iyer
fields.bio: Dr. Suresh Iyer is a top orthopedic surgeon with a focus on sports injuries and joint replacements.

fields.name: Dr. Kavita Sharma
fields.bio: Dr. Kavita Sharma is a dedicated pediatrician who specializes in child healthcare and developmental disorders.

fields.name: Dr. Anil Saxena
fields.bio: Dr. Anil Saxena has extensive experience in treating neurological disorders, focusing on stroke and epilepsy management.

fields.name: Dr. Neha Mehta
fields.bio: Dr. Neha Mehta is a well-known gynecologist, helping women through various stages of life with care and compassion.

fields.name: Dr. Rajiv Nair
fields.bio: Dr. Rajiv Nair is a skilled gastroenterologist with a focus on digestive health and endoscopy procedures.

fields.name: Dr. Anjali Reddy
fields.bio: Dr. Anjali Reddy is a specialist in endocrine disorders, treating diabetes, thyroid, and hormonal imbalances.

fields.name: Dr. Vishal Kapoor
fields.bio: Dr. Vishal Kapoor is an expert ophthalmologist, focusing on eye surgeries and vision correction.

fields.name: Dr. Shruti Desai
fields.bio: Dr. Shruti Desai specializes in mental health treatment, offering therapy and medication management for various psychological disorders.
